ay we have fellowship with him while we walk in", "But may", "darkness, we lie and do not practice the truth.", "Unison: But if we walk in the light, as he is in the light, we have", "find", "fellowship with one another, and the blood of Jesus his Son cleanses", "Thou", "us from all sin.\u201d", "Though", "In love", "*Invocation", "Apply", "*Lord's Prayer", "by", "to the Lord, the Almighty\u201d *Hymn - \u201cPraise #53", "and", "We", "\u2013 Word of Greeting Please pass the Friendship Registers found on the right", "We are", "end of each row.", "poor", "\u2013 Responsive Reading 1 Peter 2:1-12 p.1014 in Pew Bible", "Morning Prayer Ruling Elder Don Murdock", "Blessed", "\u2013 *Hymn \u201cMarvelous Grace of Our Loving Lord\u201d #465", "\u2013 \u2013 *Confession of Faith The Nicene Creed p.846 in Trinity Hymnal *Hymn", "*Benediction", "\u2013 *Doxology #731 *Postlude", "Offering", "\u2013 Offertory Anthem \u201cThe Good Shepherd\u201d Van De Water", "Soloist - Julie Covert, Piano - Alex Pinegar", "(Children 4 up until age 6 may be dismissed to Children\u2019s Church)", "\u2013 Scripture Reading Psalm 23 p.458 in Pew Bible", "Sermon The Reverend Mr. David G. McKay", "\u201cSURELY GOODNESS AND MERCY\u201d", "Response from The Valley of Vision", "OF GLORY, DIVINE MAJESTY,", "perfection adorns thy nature and sustains thy throne;", "heavens and earth are thine,", "world is thine and its fullness...", "us to place our happiness in thee, the blessed God,", "seeking life among the dead things of earth;", "we prize the light of thy smile,", "implore the joy of thy salvation,", "our heaven in thee.", "hast attended to our happiness more than we can do;", "we are fallen creatures thou hast not neglected us.", "and pity thou hast provided us a saviour;", "his redemption to our hearts,", "justifying our persons,", "sanctifying our natures.", "confess our transgressions, have mercy on us.", "weary, give us rest,...", "helpless, let thy strength be made perfect in our weakness,", 